            "| local.txt |      |            | ⬜ |",
            "| proof.txt |      |            | ⬜ |",
            "",
            "## 🧠 Attack Path (LIVE)",
            "> Keep it short. This will be reused in the final report.",
            "1. ",
            "2. ",
            "3. ",
